Date: Fri, 22 Jan 2016 18:46:27 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] don't pass -Y at all to the linker

the illumos linker can't understand the "-Y/lib"... form that f_check
generates, and -Wl, cannot pass options that include commas
---
 f_check | 4 ++--
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/f_check b/f_check
index e7e4688..9b92fab 100644
--- a/f_check
+++ b/f_check
@@ -272,8 +272,8 @@ if ($link ne "") {
 	}
 
 	if ($flags =~ /^\-Y/) {
-	    $linker_L .= "-Wl,". $flags . " ";
-	    }
+	    next;
+        }
 
 	if ($flags =~ /^\-rpath\@/) {
 	    $flags =~ s/\@/\,/g;
-- 
